125
00:08:09,464 --> 00:08:14,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm not really sure if I love</i>
<i>driving that much, but...</i></b></font>

126
00:08:16,504 --> 00:08:21,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>For the past five years, come rain or snow,</i></b></font>

127
00:08:21,814 --> 00:08:25,744
