128
00:08:25,744 --> 00:08:30,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I want to see how much I'm capable of.</i></b></font>

129
00:08:30,854 --> 00:08:33,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Everyone says that the GT-R is really fast,</i></b></font>

130
00:08:33,654 --> 00:08:37,524
