<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Kind of, yeah.</b></font>

152
00:09:51,204 --> 00:09:53,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>People are making a big
deal over this at the pass!</b></font>

153
00:09:53,604 --> 00:09:55,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nakazato of the Night Kids</b></font>

154
00:09:55,534 --> 00:09:59,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and the Takahashi Brothers
are stirring up the crowd.</b></font>

155
00:09:59,044 --> 00:10:02,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But despite all that...
you are the star today, Takumi!</b></font>

156
00:10:02,514 --> 00:10:05,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wait a minute! Please...</b></font>

157
00:10:05,714 --> 00:10:08,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...don't give me a hard time.</b></font>

158
00:10:08,384 --> 00:10:12,124
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Still... you haven't changed your mind?</b></font>

159
00:10:12,124 --> 00:10:13,584
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not that.</b></font>

160
00:10:13,584 --> 00:10:16,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To tell you the truth, I wanted to go.</b></font>

161
00:10:16,724 --> 00:10:18,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--What?!
--What?!</b></font>

162
00:10:18,464 --> 00:10:23,464
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But without the car, what can I do?</b></font>

163
00:10:23,464 --> 00:10:26,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was very depressed until you arrived.</b></font>

164
00:10:26,534 --> 00:10:28,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Gee! Why is this happening?</b></font>

165
00:10:28,874 --> 00:10:30,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How disappointing!</b></font>

166
00:10:30,604 --> 00:10:34,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What can we do without the car?</b></font>

167
00:10:34,044 --> 00:10:36,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I've got an idea! Hey, Takumi.</b></font>

168
00:10:36,214 --> 00:10:38,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How about running in Kenji's 180?</b></font>

169
00:10:38,884 --> 00:10:40,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Great idea!</b></font>

170
00:10:40,244 --> 00:10:41,884
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's the same FR...</b></font>

171
00:10:41,884 --> 00:10:44,084
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...and it's got turbo for extra power...</b></font>

172
00:10:44,084 --> 00:10:46,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It sure will run fast if you drive it.</b></font>

173
00:10:46,724 --> 00:10:50,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--It won't work.
--Why not?</b></font>

174
00:10:50,324 --> 00:10:54,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm not gonna race in somebody else's car.</b></font>

175
00:10:54,064 --> 00:10:58,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's gotta be my own car that I'm used to.</b></font>

176
00:10:58,134 --> 00:11:00,504
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You have a point.</b></font>

177
00:11:00,504 --> 00:11:03,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Driving somebody else's car</b></font>

178
00:11:03,004 --> 00:11:06,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>is not a good thing in the racing world.</b></font>

179
00:11:06,274 --> 00:11:09,514
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, I'll wait until the last minute.</b></font>

180
00:11:09,514 --> 00:11:11,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's my only option.</b></font>

181
00:11:15,754 --> 00:11:18,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's late. What's going on?</b></font>

182
00:11:19,754 --> 00:11:22,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's already 9:45.</b></font>

183
00:11:22,394 --> 00:11:24,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I guess he's not coming.</b></font>

184
00:11:27,434 --> 00:11:28,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Where is he?</b></font>

185
00:11:28,934 --> 00:11:31,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--What time is it?
--Almost 10:00.</b></font>

186
00:11:31,564 --> 00:11:34,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, no! He's not gonna make it!</b></font>

187
00:11:34,104 --> 00:11:36,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Where are you, Dad?</i></b></font>

188
00:11:36,434 --> 00:11:38,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Please come back!</i></b></font>

189
00:11:38,874 --> 00:11:41,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't have any more time!</i></b></font>

190
00:11:52,624 --> 00:11:55,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--He's back!
--What?</b></font>

191
00:11:55,294 --> 00:11:57,254
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Turning off of the highway...</b></font>

192
00:11:57,254 --> 00:12:00,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...gunning the engine twice,
that rhythm... and that roar...</b></font>

193
00:12:02,164 --> 00:12:04,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's here.</b></font>

194
00:12:19,344 --> 00:12:21,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can tell that just from the exhaust sound?</b></font>

195
00:12:21,014 --> 00:12:23,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you sure it's your car?</b></font>

196
00:12:23,414 --> 00:12:26,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Of course I am. It's absolutely my car!</b></font>

197
00:12:29,454 --> 00:12:31,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Takahashi Brothers are here.</b></font>

198
00:12:31,794 --> 00:12:32,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

199
00:12:32,964 --> 00:12:35,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They must be very anxious about this race.</b></font>

200
00:12:36,864 --> 00:12:41,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>They told me to my face that I'd lose.</b></font>

201
00:12:42,474 --> 00:12:44,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Damn Ryosuke Takahashi!</b></font>

202
00:12:44,574 --> 00:12:48,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's not as good as his reputation suggests.</b></font>

203
00:12:48,374 --> 00:12:51,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll beat the Eight-Six right in front of him</b></font>

204
00:12:51,244 --> 00:12:53,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>and embarrass him.</b></font>

205
00:12:53,444 --> 00:12:55,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Let's do it.</b></font>

206
00:12:55,154 --> 00:12:58,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>And if you show that you're
faster than the Eight-Six</b></font>

207
00:12:58,924 --> 00:13:01,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>that beat Keisuke Takahashi...</b></font>

208
00:13:01,594 --> 00:13:05,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...we can prove that we're
faster than the Red Suns.</b></font>

209
00:13:05,864 --> 00:13:11,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a good opportunity to
make the crowd realize something.</b></font>

210
00:13:11,834 --> 00:13:16,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The drift run can never beat the grip run.</b></font>

211
00:13:16,704 --> 00:13:21,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>There you go! It's like your favorite phrase.</b></font>

212
00:13:21,014 --> 00:13:22,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's a matter of course.</b></font>

213
00:13:22,544 --> 00:13:25,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The drift run is just a
performance to rile up the crowd.</b></font>

214
00:13:25,744 --> 00:13:28,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's not a technique for driving fast.</b></font>

215
00:13:28,554 --> 00:13:32,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's just like you to say it firmly.</b></font>

216
00:13:32,224 --> 00:13:34,524
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can say this, 'cause I went
through a drift stage myself</b></font>

217
00:13:34,524 --> 00:13:37,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>when I was driving the S13.</b></font>

218
00:13:37,564 --> 00:13:40,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A racer who has outgrown the
drift run can drive the fastest</b></font>

219
00:13:40,964 --> 00:13:42,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>in the grip run.</b></font>

220
00:13:42,434 --> 00:13:44,864
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>When you lost to the R32,</b></font>

221
00:13:44,864 --> 00:13:47,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it was really shocking.</b></font>

222
00:13:47,874 --> 00:13:51,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oops! That was a no-no.</b></font>

223
00:13:51,044 --> 00:13:55,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Well... I've changed since then.</b></font>

224
00:13:55,244 --> 00:13:57,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Since that monster defeated me,</b></font>

225
00:13:57,374 --> 00:14:01,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm driving better than ever before in the R32.</b></font>

226
00:14:01,314 --> 00:14:04,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You can't call yourself a street
racer if you stop pursuing races.</b></font>

227
00:14:04,924 --> 00:14:10,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can't stand everyone making such
a fuss about the drift technique.</b></font>

228
00:14:10,224 --> 00:14:12,894
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come out, Eight-Six!</b></font>

229
00:14:12,894 --> 00:14:17,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Showing off by drifting in your FR is over.</b></font>

230
00:14:17,064 --> 00:14:19,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'll prove it!</b></font>

231
00:14:19,564 --> 00:14:23,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>As usual, he doesn't show up
until the last minute.</b></font>

232
00:14:23,234 --> 00:14:26,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if he'll really show up.</b></font>

233
00:14:26,204 --> 00:14:29,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Didn't he tell you he had
no intention of coming?</b></font>

234
00:14:29,014 --> 00:14:32,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's coming.</b></font>

235
00:14:32,114 --> 00:14:34,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure of it.</b></font>

236
00:14:34,354 --> 00:14:36,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He'll definitely come.</b></font>

237
00:14:43,194 --> 00:14:45,294
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Anyway, that's the story.</b></font>

238
00:14:45,294 --> 00:14:47,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So I'm taking the car, Dad!</b></font>

239
00:14:47,634 --> 00:14:49,694
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You'd better hurry, Takumi!</b></font>

240
00:14:49,694 --> 00:14:51,964
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's almost time.</b></font>

241
00:14:51,964 --> 00:14:54,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're sorry... We're taking Takumi with us.</b></font>

242
00:14:54,734 --> 00:14:57,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We'll buy ten of your deep-fried
tofu in return when we get back.</b></font>

243
00:14:57,704 --> 00:15:00,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Th-The ones mixed with veggies, too...</b></font>

244
00:15:03,744 --> 00:15:06,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hey! Wait!</b></font>

245
00:15:10,484 --> 00:15:11,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Takumi...</i></b></font>

246
00:15:11,984 --> 00:15:14,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>His eyes looked different.</i></b></font>

247
00:15:14,354 --> 00:15:16,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>What's going on?</i></b></font>

248
00:15:20,094 --> 00:15:21,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Never mind.</i></b></font>

249
00:15:21,364 --> 00:15:24,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>With that setting, he'll do a good job.</i></b></font>

250
00:15:30,434 --> 00:15:32,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>We're almost at the pass.</b></font>

251
00:15:32,004 --> 00:15:33,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder if you can catch up.</b></font>

252
00:15:33,904 --> 00:15:36,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry to disappoint you,</b></font>

253
00:15:36,014 --> 00:15:38,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>but his car is a non-turbo 1.6.</b></font>

254
00:15:38,184 --> 00:15:40,844
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>This is a 2-liter turbo.</b></font>

255
00:15:40,844 --> 00:15:43,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whatever the case may be going downhill,</b></font>

256
00:15:43,184 --> 00:15:45,454
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it's no joke if I fall far behind him going uphill.</b></font>

257
00:15:45,454 --> 00:15:50,754
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Who do you think I am?! One of
the top three in the Speed Stars.</b></font>

258
00:15:59,604 --> 00:16:01,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Wow!</b></font>

259
00:16:01,174 --> 00:16:03,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So fast!</b></font>

260
00:16:03,134 --> 00:16:06,234
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I can do that, too.</b></font>

261
00:16:11,744 --> 00:16:13,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>To full power!</b></font>

262
00:16:13,484 --> 00:16:15,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--Oh...!
--Oh...!</b></font>

263
00:16:15,554 --> 00:16:16,714
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's gone!</b></font>

264
00:16:16,714 --> 00:16:19,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The Eight-Six has disappeared!</b></font>

265
00:16:30,694 --> 00:16:35,434
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Takumi... You were looking away</i>
<i>even during the entrance ceremony.</i></b></font>

266
00:16:42,044 --> 00:16:45,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Two minutes to 10:00.</b></font>

267
00:16:48,614 --> 00:16:52,174
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I guess they couldn't talk him into it.</i></b></font>

268
00:16:59,264 --> 00:17:02,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I should go apologize like a real man.</i></b></font>

269
00:17:06,134 --> 00:17:09,904
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Wait! Iketani told me to wait.</i></b></font>

270
00:17:09,904 --> 00:17:12,874
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I should do as I was told.</i></b></font>

271
00:17:18,344 --> 00:17:20,644
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>But this is all my fault.</i></b></font>

272
00:17:20,644 --> 00:17:23,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nothing to do with the Speed Stars.</i></b></font>

273
00:17:23,354 --> 00:17:26,684
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I should take my punishment like a man.</i></b></font>

274
00:17:34,394 --> 00:17:36,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Oh, no! There are so many of them!</i></b></font>

275
00:17:36,594 --> 00:17:39,594
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Looks like I have to roll with the punches.</i></b></font>

276
00:17:42,774 --> 00:17:47,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>This is no joke!</i></b></font>

277
00:17:47,004 --> 00:17:49,244
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I doubt they'll be willing to forgive me</i></b></font>

278
00:17:49,244 --> 00:17:52,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>if I tell them the Eight-Six isn't coming now.</i></b></font>

279
00:18:01,494 --> 00:18:03,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Apologizing on my knees won't help.</i></b></font>

280
00:18:03,394 --> 00:18:07,164
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>If worse comes to worst, I might get killed.</i></b></font>

281
00:18:07,164 --> 00:18:09,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Dad! Mom!</i></b></font>

282
00:18:09,134 --> 00:18:10,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Help me!</i></b></font>

283
00:18:10,534 --> 00:18:12,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Please, God!</i></b></font>

284
00:18:12,564 --> 00:18:14,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I haven't even done it with a girl yet.</i></b></font>

285
00:18:14,974 --> 00:18:16,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I don't wanna die a virgin.</i></b></font>

286
00:18:16,974 --> 00:18:19,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>--It's him!
--He's here!</b></font>

287
00:18:19,574 --> 00:18:23,344
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Oh, no! They found me!</i></b></font>

288
00:18:23,344 --> 00:18:26,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>It's too late to run.</b></font>

289
00:18:26,144 --> 00:18:28,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'm dead!</i></b></font>

290
00:18:43,734 --> 00:18:46,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What the hell are you doing</b></font>

291
00:18:46,104 --> 00:18:48,834
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>sitting in the middle of the road, Itsuki?</b></font>

292
00:18:48,834 --> 00:18:51,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Ta... Ta... Ta...</b></font>

293
00:18:51,604 --> 00:18:53,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Get out of my way!</b></font>

294
00:18:53,074 --> 00:18:57,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Come on! I'm gonna run you over.</b></font>

295
00:18:57,374 --> 00:18:59,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi!</b></font>

296
00:18:59,044 --> 00:19:01,284
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You came!</b></font>

297
00:19:01,284 --> 00:19:02,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah...</b></font>

298
00:19:02,654 --> 00:19:05,784
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Sorry, Itsuki... for being late.</b></font>

299
00:19:05,784 --> 00:19:08,794
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi...!</b></font>

300
00:19:08,794 --> 00:19:13,624
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>A street racer should race
if he's challenged, right?</b></font>

301
00:19:13,624 --> 00:19:16,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi...!</b></font>

302
00:19:17,794 --> 00:19:21,324
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Don't... Your snot... Hey, stop, Itsuki!</b></font>

303
00:19:22,734 --> 00:19:25,974
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Yeah... That's the spirit!</b></font>

304
00:19:31,044 --> 00:19:33,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Hello, this is Fujiwara Tofu.</b></font>

305
00:19:33,144 --> 00:19:36,314
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Oh, Yuichi!</b></font>

306
00:19:36,314 --> 00:19:38,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Are you there?</b></font>

307
00:19:38,354 --> 00:19:41,224
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I wonder what happened to my son.</b></font>

308
00:19:41,224 --> 00:19:44,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He wanted to go to the pass of his own accord.</b></font>

309
00:19:44,354 --> 00:19:47,094
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Like father, like son, huh?</b></font>

310
00:19:47,094 --> 00:19:50,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Putting that aside,
today his opponent is a GT-R.</b></font>

311
00:19:50,394 --> 00:19:53,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Honestly, does he have a chance?</b></font>

312
00:19:53,104 --> 00:19:55,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He really did show up.</b></font>

313
00:19:55,404 --> 00:19:58,674
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Keisuke, you were right.</b></font>

314
00:19:58,674 --> 00:20:00,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So it seems...</b></font>

315
00:20:00,944 --> 00:20:03,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You were gonna tell that Eight-Six's driver</b></font>

316
00:20:03,014 --> 00:20:06,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>about the R32's weak point, weren't you?</b></font>

317
00:20:06,184 --> 00:20:09,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I was, but not anymore.</b></font>

318
00:20:09,054 --> 00:20:12,554
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Once I saw his face, I felt nothing but disgust.</b></font>

319
00:20:12,554 --> 00:20:17,214
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>He's my enemy, after all. Besides...</b></font>

320
00:20:18,224 --> 00:20:23,024
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...he won't lose, even if he doesn't
know the R32's weak point.</b></font>

321
00:20:24,034 --> 00:20:26,134
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Did you give him any advice?</b></font>

322
00:20:26,134 --> 00:20:32,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Nothing special, but even
the GT-R has a weak point.</b></font>

323
00:20:32,374 --> 00:20:34,374
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The R32's weak point is...</b></font>

324
00:20:34,374 --> 00:20:37,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Put simply... the body weight...</b></font>

325
00:20:37,274 --> 00:20:40,814
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>...the understeer resulting
from being super front-heavy.</b></font>

326
00:20:40,814 --> 00:20:43,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even with a tuned pedal
and driving technique,</b></font>

327
00:20:43,654 --> 00:20:45,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>this basic fact doesn't change.</b></font>

328
00:20:45,724 --> 00:20:47,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you keep driving tough on the downhill,</b></font>

329
00:20:47,724 --> 00:20:50,724
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the front tires and brakes
will wear out for sure.</b></font>

330
00:20:50,724 --> 00:20:53,764
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Even with a tuned brake,</b></font>

331
00:20:53,764 --> 00:20:56,064
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>by the time they come
to the bottom of the hill,</b></font>

332
00:20:56,064 --> 00:21:00,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it'll have trouble with the
understeer going into the turn.</b></font>

333
00:21:03,434 --> 00:21:05,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If there is any chance of winning,</b></font>

334
00:21:05,604 --> 00:21:08,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it's in the corners towards
the end of the course.</b></font>

335
00:21:09,174 --> 00:21:13,444
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Whether or not the Eight-Six can
keep up with the R32 until then...</b></font>

336
00:21:13,444 --> 00:21:15,854
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's the key to this race.</b></font>

337
00:21:15,854 --> 00:21:18,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>About the Eight-Six's foot settings...</b></font>

338
00:21:18,054 --> 00:21:19,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I changed the settings a little bit.</b></font>

339
00:21:19,924 --> 00:21:22,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>The foot settings? How?</b></font>

340
00:21:25,564 --> 00:21:28,364
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>So that it will heavily understeer
when you step on the gas pedal.</b></font>

341
00:21:28,364 --> 00:21:30,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>That's how the foot setting is now.</b></font>

342
00:21:30,534 --> 00:21:33,604
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What?! Understeer by
punching the accelerator?!</b></font>

343
00:21:33,604 --> 00:21:35,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>Takumi's driving uses drift.</b></font>

344
00:21:35,704 --> 00:21:37,704
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>What were you thinking, Bunta?</b></font>

345
00:21:37,704 --> 00:21:41,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>How can he race with that
foot setting against the GT-R?</b></font>

346
00:21:41,144 --> 00:21:43,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>You don't understand, Yuichi.</b></font>

347
00:21:43,614 --> 00:21:44,984
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>If you are good enough,</b></font>

348
00:21:44,984 --> 00:21:48,484
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>the understeer setting allows you
to accelerate faster when it's FR.</b></font>

349
00:21:48,484 --> 00:21:50,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>For the purpose of carrying tofu,</b></font>

350
00:21:50,414 --> 00:21:54,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it's usually set lower.</b></font>

351
00:21:54,424 --> 00:21:56,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>With this setting,</b></font>

352
00:21:56,654 --> 00:21:59,654
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>it's possible to drive longer at full power.</b></font>

353
00:22:09,434 --> 00:22:12,204
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>But only if you're good enough...</b></font>

354
00:22:12,204 --> 00:22:14,734
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b>I'm sure he can handle it.</b></font>

355
00:22:43,774 --> 00:22:46,474
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>My pride says you gotta be wild and tough</i></b></font>

356
00:22:46,474 --> 00:22:48,544
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sou tanin wa kaizai shinai</i></b></font>

357
00:22:48,544 --> 00:22:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Never stop, tomaritakunai</i></b></font>

358
00:22:50,074 --> 00:22:52,144
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Gisei ni natta ai ga cry shite mo</i></b></font>

359
00:22:52,144 --> 00:22:53,944
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Peak mezashite, sweep the winding street</i></b></font>

360
00:22:53,944 --> 00:22:56,154
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beep beep! Keikokuon wa so cheap!</i></b></font>

361
00:22:56,154 --> 00:22:57,614
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sheep-tachi wa michi wo akero</i></b></font>

362
00:22:57,614 --> 00:23:00,054
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>'Cuz I'm never gonna stop, streak my dream</i></b></font>

363
00:23:00,054 --> 00:23:03,924
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Easy na motivation subete wa simulation</i></b></font>

364
00:23:03,924 --> 00:23:07,994
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nigetemitatte doko demo safety zone</i></b></font>

365
00:23:07,994 --> 00:23:12,004
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Nani ka wo te ni irete nani ka wo wasureteku</i></b></font>

366
00:23:12,004 --> 00:23:15,934
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sekai ga kowaretemo kawaranai</i></b></font>

367
00:23:15,934 --> 00:23:24,014
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Beasty shout, dare no te ni sae oenai</i></b></font>

368
00:23:24,014 --> 00:23:31,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hageshii yume jikan sae mo ima koeteku</i></b></font>

369
00:23:31,384 --> 00:23:35,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, yami o harisaite iku</i></b></font>

370
00:23:35,424 --> 00:23:37,394
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Like a streak to the peak</i></b></font>

371
00:23:37,394 --> 00:23:43,534
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Sekaijuu no kogekitta yoru o keshiteku</i></b></font>

372
00:23:43,534 --> 00:23:47,404
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, michi o hiraiteku</i></b></font>

373
00:23:47,404 --> 00:23:50,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Di-ding down, another round never slow down</i></b></font>

374
00:23:50,074 --> 00:23:52,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Konma zero-ichibyou de knockdown</i></b></font>

375
00:23:52,074 --> 00:23:54,274
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yoin nokoshikietekou to the next town</i></b></font>

376
00:23:54,274 --> 00:23:56,114
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Hokori mau haishachi ni hau</i></b></font>

377
00:23:56,114 --> 00:23:58,074
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rikutsu dake no nougakitachi</i></b></font>

378
00:23:58,074 --> 00:24:00,044
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Jamakusai kara shikato shitekou</i></b></font>

379
00:24:00,044 --> 00:24:02,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Streaker satte yuku street no mukou</i></b></font>

380
00:24:02,184 --> 00:24:03,384
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Something they would know</i></b></font>

381
00:24:03,384 --> 00:24:07,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, tsuzuku hatenai michi wo</i></b></font>

382
00:24:07,424 --> 00:24:11,424
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Ai mo kako mo furimukazu</i></b></font>

383
00:24:11,424 --> 00:24:15,494
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Yukeru anata kagayaiteiru</i></b></font>

384
00:24:15,494 --> 00:24:20,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Rage your dream, ima o ikiteiru</i></b></font>

385
00:24:26,574 --> 00:24:29,574
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Mr. Nakazato, what is your chance</i>
<i>of winning against the Eight-Six?</i></b></font>

386
00:24:29,574 --> 00:24:31,414
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Can't you tell without asking?</i></b></font>

387
00:24:31,414 --> 00:24:34,744
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>You mean your R32's going to win.</i>
<i>But Ryosuke Takahashi said...</i></b></font>

388
00:24:34,744 --> 00:24:37,184
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>He's just a coward since his brother lost!</i></b></font>

389
00:24:37,184 --> 00:24:41,354
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I will teach them that I, Takeshi</i>
<i>Nakazato, am the fastest in Gunma.</i></b></font>

390
00:24:41,354 --> 00:24:46,564
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>I'll show them once and for all that</i>
<i>grip driving is better than drifting!</i></b></font>

391
00:24:46,564 --> 00:24:50,634
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>--What does...</i>
<i>--It means action, action!</i></b></font>

392
00:24:50,634 --> 00:24:54,104
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Next time on Initial D, "Battle to the Limit!"</i></b></font>

393
00:24:54,104 --> 00:24:56,034
<font face="Open Sans Semibold" size="73"><b><i>Don't miss it!</i></b></font>

